\v 11 ‘\add Because you have refused to hear our message, we(exc) will not only leave\add*, \w we|strong="G2249"\w* \w will|strong="G2316"\w* \w also|strong="G2532"\w* shake \w off|strong="G1537"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w dust|strong="G2868"\w* \w of|strong="G1537"\w* \w your|strong="G2532"\w* \w town|strong="G4172"\w* \w that|strong="G3754"\w* \w clings|strong="G2853"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w our|strong="G2316"\w* sandals, \w to|strong="G1519"\w* warn \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \add that God will reject/punish you\add*. \w But|strong="G2532"\w* \add we want you to know that\add* \w it|strong="G2532"\w* \w is|strong="G3588"\w* almost \add the time when\add* \w God|strong="G2316"\w* \w will|strong="G2316"\w* start \w to|strong="G1519"\w* rule!’
\v 12 \w I|strong="G1161"\w* \w will|strong="G1510"\w* \w tell|strong="G3004"\w* \w you|strong="G4771"\w* \w this|strong="G3588"\w*: \w On|strong="G1722"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* [MTY] \add final\add* \w day|strong="G2250"\w* \w when|strong="G1161"\w* \add God judges everyone\add*, \w he|strong="G1161"\w* \w will|strong="G1510"\w* punish \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w wicked|strong="G3588"\w* \w people|strong="G1510"\w* [MTY] \w who|strong="G3588"\w* \w long|strong="G2250"\w* ago \w lived|strong="G1510"\w* \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w Sodom|strong="G4670"\w*, \add the city that he destroyed because its people were so wicked\add*. \w But|strong="G1161"\w* \w he|strong="G1161"\w* \w will|strong="G1510"\w* punish \add even\add* \w more|strong="G1161"\w* severely \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w people|strong="G1510"\w* [MTY] \w of|strong="G2250"\w* \w any|strong="G1722"\w* \w town|strong="G4172"\w* \add whose people refused to hear your message\add*!”
