\v 13 “\w There|strong="G2532"\w* \w will|strong="G2532"\w* \w be|strong="G1096"\w* terrible \add punishment\add* \w for|strong="G3754"\w* \add you people who live in\add* [MTY] \w Chorazin|strong="G5523"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* Bethsaida \add cities\add*. \w I|strong="G2532"\w* \w did|strong="G2532"\w* \w great|strong="G2532"\w* \w miracles|strong="G1411"\w* \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w your|strong="G2532"\w* cities \add to show God’s power, but you did not turn from your sinful behavior\add*. \w If|strong="G1487"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w miracles|strong="G1411"\w* \w that|strong="G3754"\w* \w I|strong="G2532"\w* \w performed|strong="G1096"\w* \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w your|strong="G2532"\w* \add cities\add* \w had|strong="G2532"\w* \w been|strong="G1096"\w* \w done|strong="G1096"\w* \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w Tyre|strong="G5184"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w Sidon|strong="G4605"\w* \add cities\add*, \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w wicked|strong="G3588"\w* \w people|strong="G3588"\w* \w who|strong="G3588"\w* \w lived|strong="G2532"\w* \w there|strong="G2532"\w* \w would|strong="G1096"\w* \w have|strong="G2532"\w* \w long|strong="G3819"\w* \w ago|strong="G3819"\w* \add shown that they were sorry for their sins by\add* \w sitting|strong="G2521"\w* \w on|strong="G1722"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* ground wearing coarse cloth \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w putting|strong="G2532"\w* \w ashes|strong="G4700"\w* \w on|strong="G1722"\w* \w their|strong="G2532"\w* heads.
